      "role": "user",
      "content": "those are valid points, but it's still hard to wrap my head around how an entire settlement could just leave no trace of what happened. like, if it was a raid or a disease, wouldn't there be some record of it in other archives or local newspapers from the time? why do these specific gaps feel so... empty?",
